{"tid":2063594,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【反修例一周年】被標籤藍店負責人：生意至今未有改善","createTime":"2020-06-14T06:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T07:09:40.000Z","uid":134683,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1c796a0e9d9ea006ccbf0cd9b8d6c4af6c5a31b3","tid":2063594,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:44:04.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】反修例運動期間，社會出現黃色經濟圈，一些中資或被視為撐警的被標籤為「藍店」，部分遭破壞或受抵制。<br />\n<br />\n在大埔賣腸粉的王莉莉，以前生意不錯，但一場反修例運動，她的生意一落千丈。<br />\n<br />\n去年六月底，有團體舉行撐警集會，王莉莉帶同兩個兒子參加，並放上FACEBOOK，從此被網民標籤為「藍店」。<br />\n<br />\n事隔一年，至今生意仍未有好轉。為彌補損失，她除了賣腸粉，還賣糖水、小菜。<br />\n<br />\n除了生意減少，王莉莉更稱，過去一年，不斷有人向食環署、消防處等部門投訴她的店舖。<br />\n<br />\n對於被指撐警，她表示，至今不會改變立場，因為這也是言論自由的體現。她希望不同立場的人可理性溝通，減少社會兩極化 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=394375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394375&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=1beebde9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394375&h=914a89ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=394375</a>"},{"pid":"638672312438f3cb5cb514d724fbfd9481a3ae19","tid":2063594,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:44:50.000Z","msg":"出嚟做天使嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760f083ca46d8410c382de3d4ccd74e773cd964b","tid":2063594,"uid":315268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:46:21.000Z","msg":"而家啲中年真係一啲都唔捱得"},{"pid":"f5df28f75b65e138348591ca06f39c3b47c34cb8","tid":2063594,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cSh32iG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSh32iG.jpg&h=310adc70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5316780bcc02ed92d9017b3cc6799a356f7c3004","tid":2063594,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:48:23.000Z","msg":"個兩個兒子真慘，<br />\n有D咁既老母，迫去奶狗"},{"pid":"f4fdc357b3c4bcaa1af1fd9d293546b88d77deeb","tid":2063594,"uid":66324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:51:14.000Z","msg":"又係呢間, 乜得呢間藍店渣咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e4f4fbdf62ed633b1bf60eb54866817c29d143","tid":2063594,"uid":320041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:54:07.000Z","msg":"幾時再攪撐警集會?點解冇哂聲氣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0aaad78eeaf14ccd59d415ebde034a248a5a92","tid":2063594,"uid":28446,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:56:45.000Z","msg":"我地尊重你言論自由 希望你都尊重我地消費自由<br />\n撐得警就唔好怨 要預左做過街老鼠<br />\n要生存就要加入黃色經濟圈"},{"pid":"412d02e6847bd6e1b6e967524ddd49951a2d2d9e","tid":2063594,"uid":252142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T06:57:52.000Z","msg":"聽日我去大大力罰佢"},{"pid":"0273580a14ac06c8896e0fe26ed39575d0085f16","tid":2063594,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:01:40.000Z","msg":"唔自貼上fb咪冇事<br />\n根本就死於自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6649594572fae5e6105f27a0887ec79536b499","tid":2063594,"uid":300679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:03:58.000Z","msg":"佢所謂既理性溝通咪又係屌鳩黃絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8f8ba7db0129d69c03fce0f13c1897bb0b7b97","tid":2063594,"uid":324041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"咁多藍絲撐警，同路人冇理由冇生意㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}